HEADWORD: Macropinacoid
<hw>Mac`ro*pin"a*coid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Macro-</ets> + <ets>pinacoid</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Crystallog.)</fld> <def>One of the two planes of an orthorhombic
crystal which are parallel to the vertical and longer lateral
(macrodiagonal) axes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Macropod</ent>⟦br⟧
